    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend trips. You'll love how smooth it drives! It's got a few tiny signs of love here and there, but overall it looks fantastic and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 29500.0,
