    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to its 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power through a variable M-differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for superior lateral grip and chassis communication. A purist\u2019s example optimized for tactile feedback and kinetic performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
