    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2019 mid-size SUV that has served as a reliable family vehicle. The exterior finished in Metallic Slate remains vibrant; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger bumper, the body is straight and free of any major dents or rust. Inside, the Charcoal leather upholstery has been meticulously cared for\u2014no rips, stains, or odors, as this has always been a pet-free and non-smoking cabin. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in solid shape with a complete service history available. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and replaced the front brake rotors. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. It drives smooth, shifts effortlessly, and is ready for its next owner without any immediate maintenance needs. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manual.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
